high_descs: Turn right and walk straight. Then take a left turn to enter into the bathroom and turn towards the sink.
Take the fork from the sink.
Make a right turn towards the bowl.
Put the fork in the small bowl which is already placed in the bathtub.
Take the small bowl along with the fork.
Turn right side towards the sink.
Place the small bowl along with the fork in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the fork and bowl in the SinkBasin.

high_descs: Turn right and go straight to reach the sink in the bathroom.
Pick up the fork from the sink.
Turn left to the bowl on your right.
Put the fork on the bowl kept on the bathtub.
Collect the pan along with the bowl.
Turn right to reach the sink.
Put the bowl along with the fork into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the pan along with the fork into the SinkBasin.

high_descs: Turn around to head down the passage and turn left to reach the bathroom sink.
Pick up the fork from the sink.
Turn left to reach the bowl.
Put the fork in the bowl.
Pick up the bowl from the tub.
Turn right to the sink.
Put the bowl in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the Fork in the Bowl and place it in the SinkBasin.
